Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.02,0:01:39.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh... Sekarang sudah siang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:45.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:46.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:52.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Samponya di mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:54.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang kanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:55.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:06.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang biru lebih cocok.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tim pecah kuning telur, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:18.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan kau ini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:24.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ingin menantangku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:25.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:26.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudnya ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:28.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan tanya aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:30.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tiba-tiba ke sini pagi ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:33.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Intinya adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:35.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai-lah yang akan menikahi Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:36.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serius?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:37.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baru dengar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:40.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak paham mendengar lanturanmu itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:41.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Intinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:45.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai adalah teman semasa kecilnya Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:47.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan jadi masalah kalau dia punya tunangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:48.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:52.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,kalau Ai menang,\Nbisakah kau menjauh dari Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:56.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:59.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,kami bertunangan itu\Nkarena keinginan orang tua kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan kami yang...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:04.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:06.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menerima tantanganmu itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:10.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Amano?! Berarti kau mau?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lupakan dulu soal Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:15.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku terganggu kalau dia terus mengikutiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:19.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau aku menang,\Njangan mendekati rumah ini lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:20.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dimengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, tunggu dulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:27.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertandingan dart?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:28.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:31.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin juga kita adu jotos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:31.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:34.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu akan berdampak ke pekerjaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:38.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pilihan tepat untuk\Nkita bisa mengenal satu sama lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:39.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,\Npekerjaan apa yang kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu-tunggu, Mau bisbol, kah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pakai tangan kiri lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menyanyikan lagu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:52.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:55.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sampai tidak bisa komentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:56.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:59.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga mengunggah foto, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:01.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lemparan kedua.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:02.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selanjutnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:06.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,apa kau akan pindah ke SMA kami\Nsetelah musim panas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:09.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak akan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:14.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku masuk universitas\Ndi usia 13 tahun dan sudah lulus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hal seperti itu mungkin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:18.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di luar negeri lazim, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:23.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau tidak salah, dulu dia pernah\Nmau direkrut suatu organisasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kapan-kapan minta ajari belajar, ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lemparan ketiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:32.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terakhir, apa yang membuatmu\Ningin menikahi Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:36.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meleset!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:42.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Giliranmu.\N- Kau tidak mau jawab?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:44.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habis, tadi meleset.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aturan apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kulempar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:54.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Dia kunci sikutnya?!\N- Auranya luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:59.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, apa kau\Nbenar-benar berniat menikahi Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Langsung ke situ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sendiri yang akan memilih calonku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:11.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:14.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selanjutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau sudah pernah seks dengan Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Sudah, ya.\N- Tidak, lah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:25.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku pernah lihat alat kelaminnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:27.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai juga pernah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dulu sebelum pubertas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah hentikan soal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ke pertanyaan terakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:40.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau menyukai Nagi, atau membencinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:43.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertanyaan macam apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yang bertanya di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:48.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak keduanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:51.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu kita buat begini saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:57.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau lemparanmu kena sasaran,\Nartinya kau menyukainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:57.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:01.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari tadi meleset terus,\Nmana mungkin tiba-tiba kena sasaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:10.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tampaknya kita tak perlu lihat hasilnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:14.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagi Ai, musuh terberat sepertinya adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:17.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Hm?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:19.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kok bisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana kutahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:23.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hasilnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:30.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku sudah paham keadaannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:32.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai pamit pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:33.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:37.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu dulu, Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:41.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Amano, tolong jaga Sachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:44.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa juga dia bilang begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:49.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku tidak sangka\Ndia bilang kau musuh terberatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:52.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai dari dulu orangnya aneh, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:59.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dipermainkan oleh takdir, katamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:06:59.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau salah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:05.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sedang menghadapi takdirku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:09.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di mataku, kau tampak\Nmeronta-ronta tanpa tujuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi, kau itu tunanganku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:14.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku punya tunangan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:16.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak, jangan menikah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa benar begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai akan memberitahumu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:28.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,mengenai takdir berbentuk rawa\Ndi mana kau sedang terjebak sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:29.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:36.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini gawat, kalau begini aku akan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:39.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tempat itu sungguh\Nmenggelisahkan dan menakutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:42.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang semangat, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bertahanlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:46.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan tinggalkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:51.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian berempat\Nselalu meronta-ronta seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kalian tidak sadar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:08:01.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian bisa bangkit\Ndengan mudah di rawa ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:05.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan kalian bahkan bisa keluar kapan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:10.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau bisa pasti sudah kulakukan dari dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:13.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, biar kuubah penyampaiannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:16.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maukah kau berhenti hadapi takdir yang pilu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan menuju ke tahap berikutnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:19.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:21.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi sekarang 17 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai sekarang 18 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:28.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Artinya, sebentar lagi\Nkita akan bisa menikah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:30.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, itu benar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:35.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu artinya dari detik ini\Nkau akan bahagia kalau bersama Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:38.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Intinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:43.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai benar-benar mencintaimu, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:48.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:51.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Kalau begitu, Ai pulang dulu.\N- Ai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:52.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:56.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:59.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:07.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini pertama kalinya\Naku ditembak oleh perempuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:17.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dalam hidupku, baru kali ini aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:20.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Badanku panas...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:21.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu cuma kepanasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:26.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau tidak segera makan sesuatu\Nnanti benaran ambruk, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:30.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak dari tadi malam\Ntidak makan apa-apa, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:33.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat ini, aku merebus somen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau merebus tanpa\Nmelepas kertas pengikatnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi lucu juga kalau dipikir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tepar hanya karena ditembak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:45.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benaran, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:48.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak SD zaman sekarang saja\Ntidak sampai sebegitunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:50.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berisik kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:52.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masih keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:55.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, ini baru pertama kalinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:56.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ditembak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:58.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal kau tukang nembak?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:00.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi sedih dengarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:02.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka ini kenapa coba?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:04.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nembak-ditembak, ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:08.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau sudah terbiasa,\Nmalah menghindar sebelum ditembak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:12.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malah jadi harus tenang,\Nsoalnya harus pikir cara tolaknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:14.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar, tuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:17.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian salah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:23.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pernyataan cintanya Ai berbeda\Ndengan orang iseng di cerita kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:26.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia menembakku setelah\Nmemendam perasaannya selama 7 tahun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:29.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ribet ini, mah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Delusinya lumayan kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi, Nagi benar-benar ditembak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata Ai yang nembak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:40.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, aku akan merebus somen tambahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:43.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan buat sup buat somennya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:49.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak menyangka ditembak\Nbisa membuat seseorang seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Aku menyukaimu, Segawa."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:55.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Maukah kau berpacaran denganku?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:01.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa Segawa dulu juga jadi seperti ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:05.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Jangan ada rahasia-rahasiaan lagi."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:10.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Umino, apa maksudmu\Nkau ditembak oleh perempuan lain?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:13.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin lihat Segawa seperti itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:16.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, aku harus bikin dia tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lo, ada Umino?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:25.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:27.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:29.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada sesuatu, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:31.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau menghalangi, bisa minggir tidak?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:33.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:38.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan ada festival di kuilku mulai besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kedengarannya berat, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:46.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai tahun ini aku jadi penanggung jawab.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:48.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari pagi sudah sibuk sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:51.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, jadi seperti itu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, apa yang ingin kau bicarakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:57.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, aku jadi lupa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan perkara besar, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:04.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong letakkan di bawah panggung!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, kau bilang apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:12.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan perkara yang tidak besar, mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:17.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi begitu ceritanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:20.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu pertama kalinya\Naku ditembak dalam hidupku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:23.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang menembakku adalah teman masa kecilku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:26.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan aku jadi kegirangan sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:28.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlebih, aku berdebar karenanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:34.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:40.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana, Segawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:41.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau jadi gelisah, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:44.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku kelewatan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:47.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:49.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang aku dibuat berdebar,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:52.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi aku takkan berpaling darimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:57.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kuharap kau bisa tenang...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Panas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:04.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi memang pisau ini
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,sungguh sangat tajam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:13.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin aku harus bunuh seseorang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bercanda, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:21.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sebenarnya ingin memberitahumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.04,tanda_srt,,0,0,0,,FESTIVAL NORYO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:23.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:29.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Besok aku ingin kau datang\Nke festival dengan Erika, Sachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:31.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan teman masa kecilmu itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:47.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat, itu panggungnya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:49.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kelihatan seperti mau konser.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:52.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tarian Bon sekarang sudah maju, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:56.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak berani mengajak Ai kemari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:01.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian satu rombongan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:05.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai, kenapa di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:09.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dengar ada festival terkenal,\Njadi aku ikut berpartisipasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:10.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benarkah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:15.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak sabar karena sudah lama\Ntidak ke festival di Jepang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:19.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apalagi, aku bisa datang bersama Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:22.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, Ai, bisa kau menjauh dariku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:29.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino, kau sudah datang, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:33.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anu, ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:35.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:38.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini teman sekelasku, Segawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:41.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini teman masa kecilku, Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:45.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harap kalian berdua bisa akur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:47.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Salam kenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:49.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Salam kenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:52.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mata mereka seram.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:56.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus siap mati\Nhentikan mereka jika ada apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:15:00.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Kalau begitu, ayo keliling berlima.\N- Apa kau gila?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, aku ada sambutan panitia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:04.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:11.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mau ikut, 'kan?\NKe lomba cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:13.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ikut.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:15.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cosplay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:17.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak diberi tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:19.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat barang bawaan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Salah satu daya tarik festival ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:25.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lomba cosplay terbuka untuk umum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:29.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hadiahnya adalah\Ndua tiket masuk taman bermain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:30.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ditambah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino akan jadi jurinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:35.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mohon kerja samanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:39.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku jadi juri?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:42.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak akan diam dengar ada cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:44.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akulah yang akan menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin ke taman bermain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:48.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan buat Nagi terkesan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aroma medan perang...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:56.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian sudah menyiapkan\Nyang kusebut di pesan kemarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:16:00.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian berdua mengerti, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:05.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya tiba saatnya\Nsalah satu acara utama
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:08.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lomba cosplay dimulai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:11.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin karena ada\Nbintang tamu di acara berikutnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:14.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,banyak media-media yang datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pembawa acaranya adalah saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:20.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yonezawa dari\Nklub penyiar SMA Megurogawa dan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:23.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Takahashi yang akan memandu acara ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:27.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak lupa, jurinya\Nadalah mereka bertiga dan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:32.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Suara dari kalian para penonton!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi, lama tak bertemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hiro yang memanggilku kemari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:44.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlalu banyak orang yang kukenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:46.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demi memangkas anggaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lupakan soal alasannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:50.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa aku jadi jurinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:52.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa mungkin Segawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:54.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia berniat untuk menang?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:57.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang aku pantasnya jadi nomor satu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:00.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa harus sistem voting...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:03.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa bukan aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:04.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cih.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:05.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku benci kau.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:09.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Harus memilih salah satu\Nrasanya seperti siksaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:13.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, peserta nomor 1,\Nsilakan ke panggung!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini adalah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:17.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kostum boneka kelinci?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:21.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penampilan pertama\Ntelah mengguncang konsep cosplay,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,penonton sampai tidak bisa diam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu pasti Amano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:30.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana Hiro?\NAku pakai kostum sesuai janji kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:34.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan lebih seru\Nkalau salah satu dari kita menang!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:35.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, kan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:36.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Si tidak mau kalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:39.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau mau menang\Npakai kostum "gadis kelinci"!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:40.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:42.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cosplay yang ekstrem, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:43.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tancap gas saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:46.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini bukan kostum boneka kelinci!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:47.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini gadis kelinci!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kuraih kemenangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:54.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa jadi begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:58.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa, sih?\NHarusnya kalian lebih heboh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:00.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita ke peserta selanjutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:03.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Peserta nomor 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:06.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan Sachi?\NDia berpenampilan seperti biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:07.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini adalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:11.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa sangka?!\NCosplay anak SMP!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:18.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hadiahnya tiket masuk taman bermain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:20.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mau.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:22.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau mau menang, pakai kostum "perawat"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:23.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:27.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana bisa aku menyiapkannya\Nkalau waktunya mepet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:30.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku ingin ke taman bermain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:33.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:34.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Manjai aku, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:38.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata bukan anak SMP!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:41.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi adik perempuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:46.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tak pernah sekali pun\Nbersikap seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:49.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari kita ke peserta selanjutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:51.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Peserta nomor 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:54.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga, apa yang terjadi di sini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:56.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu baru Segawa yang kukenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:19:01.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gadis kuil tampil dengan\Nbercosplay sebagai gadis kuil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:06.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar Erika dan Sachi, kalian\Nbenar-benar mengacaukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:09.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begini,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku yang akan meramaikannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:21.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hadirin sekalian, silakan datang\Nberkunjung ke Kuil Meguro Myojin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:26.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tarian seriusnya Segawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:28.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang tadi sungguh indah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Calon pemenang baru telah muncul!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:32.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gila parah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:39.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang tersisa cuma Ai sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:41.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cosplay apa dia, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:45.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang menang adalah aku.\NItu sudah pasti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:48.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Taman bermain, taman bermain,\Ntaman bermain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:50.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Panas sekali...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita lanjutkan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:54.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Peserta nomor 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:57.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu bukan cosplay, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:06.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cosplay apa sebenarnya ini?\NLolita? Atau Jiraikei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:11.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sini aku harus\Nminta maaf pada hadirin sekalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:13.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:18.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf pada para hadirin atas\Nterganggunya keseruan lomba cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:21.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Acara yang semula dijadwalkan setelah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:23.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan saya majukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:27.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm, acara berikutnya itu\Nkalau tidak salah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:29.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:31.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Tidak mungkin.\N- Jangan bilang...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:45.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah lagu ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:46.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:50.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Arus Pendek"-nya Mochizuki Ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:20:57.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, begitulah gadis virtual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:20:59.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bak tegangan misterius, aneh rasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:03.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengapa kalimat fana itu\Njatuh lalu lenyap begitu saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:05.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gila! Ambil video!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:07.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Ini benaran asli?!\N- Apa yang sedang terjadi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:11.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terkurung dalam takdir yang tak kupahami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:14.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kejar-kejaran seperti biasa...\Nantara memberi atau tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:18.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak menyerah, tak masuk akal.\NKekacauan, kekacauan, kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:21.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagu ini yang terkenal itu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:24.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini lagu yang Segawa\Nnyanyikan di tempat karaoke
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:26.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hasilkan panas...\NSekarang atau tidak sama sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:30.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sosok tak dikenal dalam memori.\NAku tak tahu harus bagaimana.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:34.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tanggapan polosmu,\Ncampuran ego dan harapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:37.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menari bersama\Nteori relativitas di malam hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.24,0:21:40.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baru saja ada pengumuman\Ndari akun resminya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:45.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keadaan tak menentu, haleluya.\NInikah yang dinamakan cinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.81,0:21:47.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keadaan tak menentu, haleluya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:48.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:53.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keadaan tak menentu, haleluya.\NBiar hati ini menyala.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:55.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak peduli meski terbakar hangus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:57.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Desir setrum
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:22:01.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sosok penyanyi-penulis lagu\Npenuh misteri, Mochizuki Ai,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:03.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,akhirnya memperlihatkan wajah aslinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:38.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hidupmu itu juga hidupku, tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.32,0:23:44.33,tanda-4,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\blur1\bord3\shad0\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(239.2,842)}Episode 5: Hidupmu Itu Juga Hidupku, Tahu?
